REFERENCE           21KYK001
LANG_ENGLISH        "I'm going with you on this one.  Rosh disappeared near Byss and it's too dangerous for anyone to go alone."
LANG_CHINESE        "这次我和你一起去。洛西就是在比斯附近失踪的,再单枪匹马地来太危险了."

REFERENCE           21JAK001
