LANG_CHINESE        "这里我感觉不到黑暗原力，凯尔."

REFERENCE           21KYK002
LANG_ENGLISH        "Me neither.  That's not good. Tavion must have been here already."
LANG_CHINESE        "我也一样，事情不妙啊，特维安肯定来过这里."

REFERENCE           21KYK003
LANG_ENGLISH        "They've got a tractor beam on us.  I can't break free!"
LANG_CHINESE        "他们对我们发射了牵引光束，我们挣脱不了了!"

REFERENCE           21KYK004
LANG_ENGLISH        "Okay here's the plan:  I served on one of these ships back in my Imperial days.  You disable the tractor beam and I'll trigger the ship's self-destruct.  Ready?"
LANG_CHINESE        "我们这么干：我原来在帝国当兵时，曾在一艘战舰上服役过。你去关掉牵引光束，\n我来想办法让这艘船自爆。听明白了吗?"

REFERENCE           21JAK002
LANG_ENGLISH        "Ready as I'll ever be."
LANG_CHINESE        "明白了."

REFERENCE           21KYK005
LANG_ENGLISH        "Find the tractor beam and disable it!"
LANG_CHINESE        "找到并关掉牵引光束！"

REFERENCE           21KYK006
LANG_ENGLISH        "What are you waiting for, an invitation?"
LANG_CHINESE        "你还在等什么，想让别人来请你？"

REFERENCE           21KYK007
LANG_ENGLISH        "Go!"
LANG_CHINESE        "出发!"

REFERENCE           21KYK008
LANG_ENGLISH        "Jan told me there would be days like this.  Get going!"
LANG_CHINESE        "简告诉我总会有这样的一天的，行动!"

REFERENCE           21KYK009
LANG_ENGLISH        "We're not gonna get out of here if you don't do your part!"
LANG_CHINESE        "如果你不把自己该做的做好，我们就出不去了!"

REFERENCE           21JAK003
LANG_ENGLISH        "Tractor beam disabled."
LANG_CHINESE        "牵引光束已关闭."

REFERENCE           21KYK010
NOTES               "(via comm)"
